This directory contains a solver for the Mkc problem using the BCP
framework.

For more details see the paper J.J.H. Forrest, J. Kalagnanam, and L. Ladanyi
"A Column-Generation Approach to the Multiple Knapsack Problem with
Color Constraints", INFORMS Journal on Computing, January 1, 2006;
18(1): 129 - 134.  

For information on how to build/use the mkc code see the INSTALL file.

For more information on BCP see https://projects.coin-or.org/Bcp.
